title: Nirvana - Complete Cover Versions
description:
Track List:

01 Here She Comes Now [From the Velvet's Tribute LP '15 Minutes].flac
02 Do You Love Me [Kiss number recorded for Seattle Radio, June'88].flac
03 Jesus Wants Me For A Sunbeam [Originally a Christian spiritual later recorded in this version by the Vaselines. This recording made in Washington 31,10,91].flac
04 Dazed And Confused [Led Zep song recorded in Europe Nov. '89].flac
05 D-7 [Live version of the Wipers song - Off Ramp Club, Seattle, Nov. '90].flac
06 Turnaround [Devo song recorded for Peel session, Jan. '91].flac
07 Return Of The Rat [Another Wipers song, this version appeared on the Tribute 7'' box set].flac
09 The Man Who Sold The World [Electric version of Bowie's song, rome 22,2,94].flac
10 Molly's Lips [Another Vaselines song, Peel session Jan. '91].flac
11 Love Buzz [Written by one 'Robby Van Leewen', Nirvana's first single live in Vancouver, March '90].flac
12 Plateau [Acoustic version of the Meat Puppets song].flac
13 Lake of Fire [as above].flac
14 Baba O'Reilly [Who song live in France, 1991].flac
15 Son Of A Gun [Another Vaselines song, Peel session Jan. '91].flac
16 Where Did You Sleep Last Night [Kurt's solo version of Leadbelly's song].flac
17 Here She Comes Now [Another version of the V.U. song, live in Seattle Nov. '90].flac
